"Oranje": "Have you made use of the Food Stand yet?"

"Eating a balanced meal can give your body that extra edge you need to take down the DOLLS!"

"I've sent you some coordinates, so go there and find some, okay?"

"Tackling your missions in earnest is good, but please remember to pace yourself."
"Please keep your health in top form, for when you really need it to be."
